senses.sense_definition: Not <w>conjugated</w>; not modified to show grammatical tense, person, or number, or not chemically combined with another substance.

examples.text: The dictionary lists the word in its <w>unconjugated</w> form so that learners can find the root meaning easily.
Doctors monitored the level of <w>unconjugated</w> bilirubin in the patient's blood to assess liver function.
